formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	The firm had not maintained separate RERA Account. Therefore, the amount collected from the customers is deposited in bank account mentioned above. Amount deposited and withdrawn from the bank account reflects only booking receipts collected and utilized in the project.
2.	In respect of the all the booked flats on the date of issuing this certificate, the firm is not in possession of Agreement to sale details and in absence of information, I have mentioned the date of sale deed executed instead of date of agreement to sale. 4.	As per guidance note-1 dated 09-07-2019, interest paid on partners capital is not considered in figure of finance cost incurred and paid above.
